POS:                    2 REC

Coinbase Maturity:      5 Blocks

Block Reward Halving:   Never

Last POW Block:         500000

POS Start:              Block 1

Minimum POS Age:        1 Hour

Maximum POS Age:        No Max

Max Coins:              7000000 REC

